Package api.options

Contains option related classes.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractOption
    The AbstractOption class represents a named option with no parameter.
    AbstractParameteredOption<T>
    The AbstractParameteredOption class represents a named option with a parameter.
    AfterOption
    The BeforeOption class represents the after option several commands have.
    BeforeOption
    The BeforeOption class represents the before option several commands have.
    NameOption
    The NameOption class represents the name option several commands have.
    TextOption
    The TextOption class represents the text option several commands have.

Package api.options Description

Contains option related classes. Most of those classes are container classes for convince access to the options and their values.
